MANY people still wonder how actress Omoni Oboli became the mother of her three sons. They look more like her siblings than her children, and she is always proud to show them off on social media. For her 44th birthday celebration on Friday, Oboli released a stunning photo. She wrote: “This is what 44 looks like. Thank you Jesus for growth.”   Ogunbayo joins the league of 50     Ondo prepares for Asun Carnival     DJ Cuppy unveils future plans   The photo quickly reminded her followers how she is cheating on nature and they all stormed her page to appreciate her. Even though she has the heart of a 44 years old woman, she seems to have the body and face of a lady in her 20s. “No way this 44,” a follower said. “You are the real ageless queen. I love you with everything.” Another follower said she had never seen a 44-year-old ‘hotter’ than Oboli.